Alll New Aug 2018 Carrier 4 ton hvac.Also new Whirlpool D/W installed. New Nov Rinnai on demand propane water heater. Has W/D both work well. Included new Toro 46 riding mower all the L/V Rm D/R furniture. 
Assumable 4.62% FHA Mortgage All detitled foundation certified.
Home has fenced backyard and lovely slate front porch looking over acre of lawn. Total 1.5 acres in Potato Creek Bay. Two private community piers and small boat launch right intp Potato Creek Fish Hatchery. Home is second row water. 
Has full two car garage built in 2009 with enclosed breezeay to house. 
Dinning room newly painted. All bedrooms oversized. 
Available by appointment Sun-Thu
